    <h3 itemprop="headline">Shrey Parikh bounces back, battles nerves and dominates spell-off to win the National Spelling Bee</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Shrey Parikh has won the Scripps National Spelling Bee, beating Ishaan Gupta in a lightning-round tiebreaker.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2026/05/29/shrey-parikh-wins-the-scripps-national-spelling-bee-beating-ishaan-gupta-in-lightning-round/"  >(Ben Nuckols, Associated Press, Local 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
