    <h3 itemprop="headline">Israeli ambassador compares France's far-left leader's rhetoric to Hitler as antisemitism surges</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      France recorded 1,320 antisemitic acts in 2025, up from 436 in 2022, as Jewish families alter daily habits to avoid being identified, CRIF&apos;s president says.
