    <h3 itemprop="headline">Aid supplies reach heart of Congo's Ebola outbreak as WHO head travels to Kinshasa</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Aid supplies have been rushed in to the center of Congo's Ebola outbreak where medical workers are struggling with equipment shortages, distrustful locals and armed groups.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2026/05/28/aid-supplies-reach-heart-of-congos-ebola-outbreak-as-who-head-travels-to-kinshasa/"  >(Justin Kabumba And Ope Adetayo, Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
