        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">NAACP&#8217;s Elegbede enters crowded Rochester mayoral race</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The field of candidates vying for the top office in the city of Rochester is getting crowded. The latest to enter is the local NAACP president, bringing the number of announced candidates to seven.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/05/22/rochester-mayoral-race-getting-crowded-as-naacps-elegbede-enters/"  >(Catharine Richert, MPR News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 22 May 2026 18:08:08 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 22 May 2026 18:08:08 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="The Associated Press, MPR News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static14/politics/2026/05/22/tulsi-gabbard-resigns-as-director-of-national-intelligence-citing-her-husbands-health.webp" alt="Gabbard resigns as director of national intelligence" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Gabbard resigns as director of national intelligence</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Tulsi Gabbard has resigned as President Donald Trump’s director of national intelligence, saying she needed to step away as her husband battles cancer. She is the fourth Cabinet official to depart during Trump’s second term.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/05/22/tulsi-gabbard-resigns-as-director-of-national-intelligence-citing-her-husbands-health/"  >(The Associated Press, MPR News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sat, 23 May 2026 12:59:03 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sat, 23 May 2026 12:59:03 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Kirsti Marohn, MPR News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static14/politics/2026/05/23/u-of-m-researchers-to-study-how-forwardfacing-sonar-could-affect-minnesota-fish.webp" alt="U researchers to study impact of forward-facing sonar" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">U researchers to study impact of forward-facing sonar</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Also known as forward-facing sonar, the technology lets anglers spot and track fish in real time. A team of researchers will study whether live-imaging sonar changes catch rates and what the long-term effects could be for fish populations in Minnesota lakes.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/05/23/u-of-m-researchers-to-study-how-forwardfacing-sonar-could-affect-minnesota-fish/"  >(Kirsti Marohn, MPR News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div></div></fieldset></main>
